title: PPPP’s Zulfiqar Bichani wins NA-217 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarian Candidate Zulfiqar Bichani has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-217 Tando Allahyar by securing 1,19,530 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Grand Democratic Alliance candidate Raheela Magsi, who bagged 73,778 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 47.77 percent.
